# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# uDOS v1.0.5.3 Comprehensive Git Exclusions
# Clean Repository Strategy - Local Files Only
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ═══════════════════════════════════════# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🎯 ADDITIONAL HEAVY EXCLUSIONS (KEEP REPO LIGHTWEIGHT)
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Desktop app (heavy dependencies, can be regenerated)
uNETWORK/display/udos-desktop/
!uNETWORK/display/udos-desktop/README.md

# Large assets and icons (can be regenerated/downloaded)
**/assets/
**/icons/
**/*.icns
**/*.ico
**/*.png
**/*.jpg
**/*.jpeg
**/*.gif

# Package locks and dependencies (can be regenerated)
package-lock.json
**/package-lock.json
Cargo.lock
**/Cargo.lock
yarn.lock
**/yarn.lock

# Documentation snapshots (can be regenerated)
docs/architecture/
docs/*-snapshot-*
docs/*-development-*

# ✅ What gets included: Essential documentation only
!docs/README.md
!docs/USER-GUIDE.md
!docs/USER-COMMAND-MANUAL.md

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ✅ WHAT GETS INCLUDED (ESSENTIAL ONLY)
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ✅ Core source code and essential scripts
# ✅ Essential documentation (README.md, LICENSE, etc.)
# ✅ Development infrastructure (dev/scripts/, .vscode/tasks.json)
# ✅ Installation scripts (install.sh)
# ✅ Template files
# ✅ Schema definitions
# ✅ Configuration templates (not user configs)═══════════════
# 🎯 GIT EXCLUSION STRATEGY
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ✅ Include: Core system, essential docs, development infrastructure
# 🚫 Exclude: All backups, logs, user data, runtime files, local installations

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# �️ ALL BACKUP FILES (COMPLETE EXCLUSION)
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Backup directories (all patterns)
backup/
backups/
**/backup/
**/backups/
dev/backups/
**/dev/backups/

# Backup files (all patterns)
*.backup
*.bak
*-backup-*
*backup*
*.tar.gz
*.tar.bz2
*.zip
*-backup.*
backup-*
**/backup-*
**/*backup*

# Hidden backup and trash patterns
.*backup*
.*trash*
.Trash*
.*bak*

# Exception: Essential backup management scripts
!dev/scripts/backup-manager.sh
!dev/scripts/lean-backup-system.sh

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 📊 ALL LOG FILES (COMPLETE EXCLUSION)
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Log directories
logs/
**/logs/
log/
**/log/

# Log files (all patterns)
*.log
*.out
*.err
*-log-*
*log*
debug.*
error.*
access.*
audit.*
security.*
**/safety-monitor.log
**/safety-monitor.pid
**/*.log
**/*.out
**/*.err

