# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# � DEVELOPMENT TOOLS (EXCLUDE CONFIGS, KEEP ESSENTIAL)
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# VS Code user settings (keep project settings)
.vscode/settings.json
.vscode/keybindings.json
.vscode/launch.json

# Git (exclude user configs)
.git/config.local
.git/hooks/

# GitHub workflow/actions
.github/

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# � SECURITY AND SENSITIVE FILES (COMPLETE EXCLUSION)
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Environment files
.env*
*.env
env.*
**/env.*

# Keys and certificates
*.key
*.pem
*.cert
*.crt
*.p12
*.pfx
id_rsa*
id_dsa*
*_rsa*
*_dsa*

# Configuration files with potential secrets
*.conf
*.config
*config*
auth.*
*auth*
credentials.*
*credentials*

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🏗️ BUILD AND RUNTIME ARTIFACTS (COMPLETE EXCLUSION)
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Build outputs
build/output/
build/dist/
dist/
**/dist/

# Runtime files
*.pid
*.lock
*.socket
*.pipe

# Process files
**/safety-monitor.pid
**/server.pid

